{"tid":255781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"返工7日通知期內違約費","createTime":"2017-05-24T05:06:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T06:14:50.000Z","uid":19808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"defa5b1ab94e73943eb34be3dcd0c54884225f7a","tid":255781,"uid":19808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:06:56.000Z","msg":"之前考完DSE我去左株式会社旗下嘅一間燒肉店做兼職（簽左約）。但因為同上司嘈交，嬲嬲地同上司講唔做，上司就同我講如果你無7日通知期內違約可能要賠錢，我就問要賠幾多同埋幾時賠，佢就同我講大約一星期內寄信比我，大約千幾蚊左右，咁當時我覺得千幾蚊可以即走我都接受，就簽紙違約。<br />\n  但之後一直都無收到信咁我當然以為唔駛賠正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但而家差唔多過左10個月左右，佢先走黎寄信比我，同埋要賠成$5000，我自問窮學生，又唔敢同父母講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n  我可唔可以用過左咁耐，同埋金額同當時我上司同我講既有出入嚟打去屌佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSorry for 1999，有啲長請見諒"},{"pid":"1ec3d5b282650e828c9feb871c840d65a8bf7f71","tid":255781,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:08:43.000Z","msg":"有冇當時錄音/whatsapp紀錄先"},{"pid":"34fa29887f028dde8842e9f9ca5ca063ded7b76c","tid":255781,"uid":19808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:11:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇當時錄音/whatsapp紀錄先</blockquote><br />\n當時係當面講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dc161af5bf94eeb073ac488cfc11ebed72ed9d8","tid":255781,"uid":35712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:12:12.000Z","msg":"on9仔 紙都簽左 仲有得懶 7日通知你都係返去hea姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />走得你咁有型呀啦"},{"pid":"5783f98c264331f7d8d37655abcfaaa07b0f787c","tid":255781,"uid":19808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:13:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>on9仔 紙都簽左 仲有得懶 7日通知你都係返去hea姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />走得你咁有型呀啦</blockquote><br />\n咁就閪啦"},{"pid":"53cbba75cc8a2a90f1fbe6f7a92f47bd94707ada","tid":255781,"uid":19808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:15:17.000Z","msg":"如果我whatsapp返之前個上司令佢承認有講過呢啲野，有無得搞"},{"pid":"d3a8bf97a2805e193eab9ffd7c6b633eaf565dc9","tid":255781,"uid":90609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:17:08.000Z","msg":"你份約有冇試用期先 自己睇下<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/public/pdf/wcp/ConciseGuide/09.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.labour.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpublic%2Fpdf%2Fwcp%2FConciseGuide%2F09.pdf&d=ENR%2BhUeR50Vy3yOqiL6HmP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=eddbf8fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/public/pdf/wcp/ConciseGuide/09.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"1633189669a4a2b3cb2e3367baa2a7c5f81530a0","tid":255781,"uid":19808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:22:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你份約有冇試用期先 自己睇下<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/public/pdf/wcp/ConciseGuide/09.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.labour.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpublic%2Fpdf%2Fwcp%2FConciseGuide%2F09.pdf&d=ENR%2BhUeR50Vy3yOqiL6HmP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=eddbf8fc\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/public/pdf/wcp/ConciseGuide/09.pdf</a></blockquote><br />\n要搵下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94ea19c209fea554562922a5f947d3f9c202db13","tid":255781,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:31:27.000Z","msg":"當係學費啦<br />\n出黎做就要鍛煉下EQ<br />\n老細唔係你老豆老母樣樣野忍你"},{"pid":"4f5b03081a229f9157ce34cebfebfc3daa671dde","tid":255781,"uid":19808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:31:55.000Z","msg":"唔識英文真可怕，虛驚sorry咁多位大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4367ba988c966f0fe56d0683fe468e49ce72de4","tid":255781,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:33:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔識英文真可怕，虛驚sorry咁多位大佬<img sr